OL,3,CMoney for long-term care could rise
OL,4,Cunder new dementia strategy
OL,6,FJersey's first dementia strategy
OL,7,Fsuggests that financial support for
OL,8,Flong-term care could be increased.
OL,10,FThe Strong Foundations strategy,
OL,11,Fcreated in partnership with Jersey's
OL,12,Fgovernment and Dementia Jersey, will
OL,13,Foutline how people with dementia will
OL,14,Fbe cared for until 2029.
OL,16,FThe government says it wants to ensure
OL,17,Fthat the long-term care scheme can
OL,18,Fsupport the costs of nursing care for
OL,19,Fpeople with dementia by the end of
OL,20,F2024.
