OL,3,CMoney for long-term care could rise
OL,4,Cunder new dementia strategy
OL,6,FHowever, they note that the financial
OL,7,Fneed to meet this is yet to be decided.
OL,9,FJersey's Health Minister Tom Binet
OL,10,Fwrote: "Most of us will be touched by
OL,11,Fdementia in our lifetimes, whether
OL,12,Fthat be through having a diagnosis
OL,13,Fourselves, caring for a family member
OL,14,For friend who has dementia, or knowing
OL,15,Fsomeone with a diagnosis of dementia.
OL,17,F"The strategy draws strongly on the
OL,18,Fvoices of islanders, particularly
OL,19,Fthose with lived experiences of
OL,20,Fdementia, whilst drawing on local and
OL,21,Fglobal evidence."
