OL,3,CMoney for long-term care could rise
OL,4,Cunder new dementia strategy
OL,6,FDementia Jersey currently estimates
OL,7,Fthat approximately 1,600 people live
OL,8,Fwith the condition in the island.
OL,10,FHowever, only five of Jersey's 56 care
OL,11,Fhomes are registered for people over
OL,12,Fthe age of 60 with dementia, providing
OL,13,Fa maximum of 271 places.
OL,15,FServices could be under strain in the
OL,16,Ffuture as government figures released
OL,17,Fin February show that dementia
OL,18,Fdiagnoses will rise by 52% by 2043.
