OL,3,CMoney for long-term care could rise
OL,4,Cunder new dementia strategy
OL,6,FThe plan outlines how the island might
OL,7,Fcope with this demand, developing
OL,8,Ffacilities to care for people with
OL,9,Fcomplex dementia needs and reducing
OL,10,Fdiagnosis waiting times to six weeks.
OL,12,FThe strategy states that diagnosing
OL,13,Fdementia early can help people "plan
OL,14,Ffor the future" and "gain access to
OL,15,Ffinancial support for their care
OL,16,Fneeds".
